devdoc.author: Lens Protocol
devdoc.details: The functions are external, so they are called from the hub via `delegateCall` under the hood.

params._profileById: A pointer to the storage mapping of profile structs by profile ID.
params._pubByIdByProfile: A pointer to the storage mapping of publications by pubId by profile ID.
params.collectModuleData: The data to pass to the publication's collect module.
params.collectNFTImpl: The address of the collect NFT implementation, which has to be passed because it's an immutable in the hub.
params.profileId: The token ID of the publication being collected's parent profile.
params.pubId: The publication ID of the publication being collected.

returns._0: uint256 An integer representing the minted token ID.

params._profileById: A pointer to the storage mapping of profile structs by profile ID.
params._profileIdByHandleHash: A pointer to the storage mapping of profile IDs by handle hash.
params.followModuleDatas: The array of follow module data parameters to pass to each profile's follow module.
params.profileIds: The array of profile token IDs to follow.

returns._0: uint256[] An array of integers representing the minted follow NFTs token IDs.

devdoc.title: InteractionLogic

collect(address,uint256,uint256,bytes,ad.notice: Collects the given publication, executing the necessary logic and module call before minting the collect NFT to the collector.

follow(address,uint256[],bytes[],mapping.notice: Follows the given profiles, executing the necessary logic and module calls before minting the follow NFT(s) to the follower.

userdoc.notice: This is the library that contains the logic for follows & collects.
